---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import advantage from "../../assets/advantage.jpg";
import sunbul from "../../assets/sunbul.svg";
import uzum from "../../assets/uzum.svg";
import teker from "../../assets/teker.svg";
---

<section class="pt-2.5 pb-12.5 lg:pt-6 bg-[rgb(245,247,247)] max-lg:px-5">
  <div
    class="container grid items-center grid-cols-1 mx-auto bg-white lg:grid-cols-2"
  >
    <div>
      <Image
        src={advantage}
        alt="advantages"
        loading="eager"
        class="max-lg:rounded-md"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="px-2.5 lg:px-9 max-lg:pt-4 max-lg:pb-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-wider">Üstünlüklərimiz</h2>
      <div
        class="text-base font-light tracking-wider mb-4 lg:mb-8 mt-1.5 lg:mt-5 text-[#363131]"
      >
        Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting
        industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's standard dummy text ever
        since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and
        scrambled it to make a type specimen book.
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-11 lg:gap-x-14 gap-y-2.5">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3.5">
          <Image src={sunbul} alt="sunbul" loading="eager" class="size-10 lg:size-12.5" />
          <h6 class="text-base tracking-wider text-[#363131]">Yüksək keyfiyyət</h6>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3.5">
          <Image src={uzum} alt="uzum" loading="eager" class="size-10 lg:size-12.5" />
          <h6 class="text-base tracking-wider text-[#363131]">Bol çeşid</h6>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3.5">
          <Image src={teker} alt="teker" loading="eager" class="size-10 lg:size-12.5" />
          <h6 class="text-base tracking-wider text-[#363131]">Bağlardan süfrənizə</h6>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
